{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"assign","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIEdgeInsets","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centerCoordinate"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":" whose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"type":"text","text":" property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the value of this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property may be overridden at any time."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The usage of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets"},{"type":"text","text":" has been deprecated"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use the map view’s property "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"},{"type":"text","text":"instead."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Changing the value of this property updates the map view immediately. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to animate the change, use the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-setContentInset:animated:completionHandler:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method instead."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"contentInset","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)contentInset","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","roleHeading":"Instance Property","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L1610","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"title":"contentInset"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view’s logical viewport.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/contentInset":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset","abstract":[{"text":"The distance from the edges of the map view’s frame to the edges of the map","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s logical viewport."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/contentInset","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"contentInset"}],"title":"contentInset","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"title":"MLNMapView","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","title":"automaticallyAdjustsContentInset","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/automaticallyadjustscontentinset","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A boolean value that indicates if whether the map view should automatically","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"adjust its content insets.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"automaticallyAdjustsContentInset"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}